    <div id="source-tab" class="content-tab-panel">
<table><tr><td>Registered Nurses' Association of Ontario (RNAO). Delirium, dementia, and depression in older adults: assessment and care. Toronto (ON): Registered Nurses' Association of Ontario (RNAO); 2016 Jul. 156 p.  [184 references]</td></tr></table>                    <p><a href="/web/20180712184633/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=50477&amp;contentType=fulltextlink&amp;redirect=http%253a%252f%252frnao.ca%252fsites%252frnao-ca%252ffiles%252f3Ds_BPG_WEB_FINAL.pdf">View the original guideline documentation</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712184633im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/></p>
