 (311), <a href="/web/20180712184633/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0278372&amp;fLockTerm=Functional+evaluation">Functional evaluation</a>
 (93.01), <a href="/web/20180712184633/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0154409&amp;fLockTerm=Major+depressive+affective+disorder%2c+recurrent+episode%2c+unspecified">Major depressive affective disorder, recurrent episode, unspecified</a>
 (296.30), <a href="/web/20180712184633/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0024517&amp;fLockTerm=Major+depressive+affective+disorder%2c+single+episode%2c+unspecified">Major depressive affective disorder, single episode, unspecified</a>
